Data Collection Method: NCDOT Count Assignments 12-07119 thru 12-07121 were counted on the same day,
with one counter assigned to each zone (aka count assignment) of the SR 1320 (Erwin Road) corridor. Counters
used Jamar count boards to count pedestrians crossing north to south and south to north across Erwin Road
within their zone. The pedestrians inside and outside the designated crosswalk were counted separately for
Count Assignments 12-07119 & 12-07121. Each zone was marked in the field and divided by traffic cones. See
the map attached on page 4 for the complete study area map of the 3 zones counted.
